<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.4.9">
<l>tāḻiyil veṇṇey taṭaṅkai yāra viḻuṅkiya</l>
<l>pēḻai vayiṟṟem pirāṉkaṇṭā yuṉṉaik kūvukiṉṟā</l>
<l>ṉāḻikoṇ ṭuṉṉai yeṟiyu maiyuṟa villaikāṇ</l>
<l>vāḻa vuṟutiyēl māma tīmakiḻn tōṭivā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Lord with a large belly who, when [his] broad hands were full,</l>
<l>devoured butter from the pot, see! He calls you.</l>
<l>Taking up a discus, he will throw [it] at you, there is no doubt, see!</l>
<l>If you want to live, Big Moon, come running joyfully!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
